description: Sun filled two bedroom, one bath condo with a spacious, private back deck! Step into an open living/kitchen area featuring custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and glass sliders leading to a large deck—ideal for outdoor entertaining. Both bedrooms fit queen-sized beds and provide ample closet space. Additional amenities include hardwood floors throughout, in-unit laundry, central A/C, and a private storage unit in the backyard. This condo is perfectly located for commuters, with easy access to the Broadway and Andrew T stations, as well as nearby highway access. Enjoy all that South Boston has to offer, from its vibrant restaurants to top attractions. This is a fantastic opportunity for first-time homebuyers and investors alike!
